        "strengths": [
          "Covers baseline locomotion, crouch, jump, hit reactions, death, and light melee punches",
          "Includes root-motion variants for roll and sword attack, which are useful for advancing actions",
          "Ships as a single GLB with one embedded texture, so browser loading is simple",
