          "UAL1.glb and UAL2.glb share the same mannequin mesh, material names, and Armature rig, so their clips can be merged onto the base fighter without retargeting"
        ],
        "limitations": [
          "No explicit guard, sidestep, backdash, kick chain, throw, launcher, wake-up, or knockdown recovery clips",
          "Only one visual identity is present, so early versus play will need cloning or mirroring",
          "The gym currently binds only a small locomotion/combat subset, so most expansion-pack clips load for future mappings rather than immediate controls",
